arStrings.szText: This seems impossible...b-but how else could...I'm sorry, I-I need a moment.
panicked, your thoughts are everywhere at once.
We confronted the demon, but were unable to harm him at all.
kind, slow and patient. You're explaining a very confusing situation.
(deep breath) If this is all true, we must find a way to destroy this demon. We should speak with Elder Suharti; she knows much about evil spirits.
you've heard some extremely difficult news. The deep breath of someone trying to process a whole lot of news at once. Pronounciation: Sue-Harr-Tee
